Actor Yul Edochie has said it is extremely childish for anyone to have a flat stomach. The last child of movie icon, Pete Edochie made this assertion in a response to a colleague’s post on Twitter. Rita Dominic tweeted that someone on the micro-blogging app wrote something which made her laugh till she became teary.   A praying wife isn’t the best – Reno Omokri     9ice, wife welcome new child     Adekunle Gold releases much anticipated album   She wrote: “Someone on this app tweeted, “having flat stomach is childish.” I laughed till tears came out of my eyes.” - Advertisement - Affirming the tweet, Yul noted having flat stomach wasn’t just childish but ‘very childish’ adding, men like himself detest such things. “True. It’s very childish. And men like us don’t like childish things”, the 40-year-old film star tweeted in response.